00:02:53.490 --> 00:02:57.140
Tunggu, dia membunuh semua petugas kita!

00:03:00.280 --> 00:03:01.390
Genkaku...

00:03:08.030 --> 00:03:10.110
Karena kau lemah?

00:03:14.830 --> 00:03:17.250
Karena itu kubilang kau hanya bisa

00:03:17.250 --> 00:03:19.540
