00:03:26.460 --> 00:03:29.760
Kenapa kalian semua hidup?

00:03:29.760 --> 00:03:31.260
Apa yg kau lakukan, Ganta?

00:03:31.260 --> 00:03:33.510
Ini takkan membuatku memaafkanmu tahu!

00:03:34.420 --> 00:03:36.680
Tolong hentikan, Nagi-sa—

00:03:37.130 --> 00:03:39.640
Aku tidak butuh kau menyelamatkanku, Ganta!

00:03:39.640 --> 00:03:41.270
Pergilah!

00:03:45.230 --> 00:03:48.550
Nee, pukulan seperti itu takkan 
membuat Shiro merasa kesakitan!

00:03:48.550 --> 00:03:49.630
Ganta!

00:03:55.980 --> 00:03:58.470
Kau itu lemah...

00:03:58.470 --> 00:04:00.400
...jadi kenapa kau...

00:04:00.570 --> 00:04:03.830
...tidak... Tidak! Ganta bodoh!

00:04:03.830 --> 00:04:05.160
Minggir! Minggir!

00:04:05.160 --> 00:04:07.250
Nagi, hentikan...

00:04:09.130 --> 00:04:12.520
Kenapa, Nagi-san?

00:04:12.520 --> 00:04:14.000
