00:04:21.780 --> 00:04:24.360
Bukankah itu yg kau katakan?!

00:04:25.050 --> 00:04:28.670
Selama kita punya harapan, 'kan?

00:04:28.670 --> 00:04:30.110
Anakku...

00:04:30.110 --> 00:04:33.640
Cahayaku sudah hilang...

00:04:33.640 --> 00:04:36.150
Hanya ada kegelapan...

00:04:36.150 --> 00:04:37.460
Dan kebencian!

00:04:37.460 --> 00:04:38.860
Ganta!

00:04:40.850 --> 00:04:42.660
Kenapa...

00:04:42.660 --> 00:04:44.580
...kau bisa bilang...

00:04:44.580 --> 00:04:46.850
