00:06:15.960 --> 00:06:17.590
Aku akan...

00:06:18.620 --> 00:06:21.590
...melindungi temanku yg sangat beharga!

00:06:36.230 --> 00:06:39.280
Temanku...

00:06:45.460 --> 00:06:46.330
Ganta?

00:06:46.620 --> 00:06:47.920
Ganta!

