00:08:25.290 --> 00:08:26.430
<i>Kenapa?</i>

00:08:27.000 --> 00:08:30.030
<i>Seorang pria yg hanya ingin menggendong anaknya...</i>

00:08:30.030 --> 00:08:31.310
<i>Kenapa?</i>

