Saatnya bekerja.

00:12:34.650 --> 00:12:37.620
Budha agung yg maha mulia.

00:12:40.460 --> 00:12:43.220
Di kota, kau berkelahi lagi, ya?

00:12:43.730 --> 00:12:49.150
Kukira kau tipe yg ramah dan pendiam.

00:12:49.770 --> 00:12:54.290
Mereka yg melakukan kejahatan hanya akan menanam kejahatan, Genkaku.

00:12:57.040 --> 00:12:59.130
